ZH: 外交官应该具备广泛的知识背景。
EN: Diplomats should have a broad knowledge base.

ZH: 外交官必须懂得如何处理复杂的国际关系。
EN: Diplomats must know how to navigate complex international relations.

ZH: 外交官需要精通多国语言。
EN: Diplomats need to be proficient in multiple languages.

ZH: 这位外交官在会议上代表了我国的立场。
EN: This diplomat represented our country's position at the meeting.

ZH: 外交官的工作需要保持中立和公正。
EN: The work of a diplomat requires maintaining neutrality and fairness.

ZH: 外交官要积极推动各国之间的合作。
EN: Diplomats should actively promote cooperation between nations.

ZH: 这名外交官在世界各地都有出色的运作记录。
EN: This diplomat has an outstanding track record of operations around the world.

ZH: 外交官必须具备出色的沟通技巧。
EN: Diplomats need to have excellent communication skills.

ZH: 这个国家派出了一批优秀的外交官参加联合会议。
EN: This country sent a group of outstanding diplomats to attend the joint conference.

ZH: 作为一名年轻的外交官，他有朝一日会成为大使。
EN: As a young diplomat, he will one day become an ambassador.

ZH: 这位外交官在处理外交事务时非常谨慎。
EN: This diplomat is very cautious when dealing with diplomatic affairs.

ZH: 外交官必须在国际关系中不断提高自己的知识水平。
EN: Diplomats must continuously improve their knowledge in international relations.

ZH: 这位外交官的谈判技巧得到了国内外的广泛认可。
EN: This diplomat's negotiation skills are widely recognized at home and abroad.

ZH: 外交官在缓解国际紧张局势中起到了关键作用。
EN: Diplomats play a crucial role in easing international tensions.

ZH: 他是一位富有经验的外交官，已经在外交领域工作了二十年。
EN: He is an experienced diplomat who has been working in the field of diplomacy for twenty years.

ZH: 这位外交官在外交政策的执行中展现了出色的领导能力。
EN: This diplomat has shown outstanding leadership in the implementation of diplomatic policies.

ZH: 外交官需要不断学习以应对未来的挑战。
EN: Diplomats need to continuously learn to meet future challenges.

ZH: 这名外交官在处理危机时表现得十分冷静和果断。
EN: This diplomat demonstrated extreme calm and decisiveness in handling the crisis.

ZH: 在国际谈判中，外交官需要有耐心和毅力。
EN: In international negotiations, diplomats need to have patience and perseverance.

ZH: 这位外交官在与外国政府的合作中展现了极高的能力。
EN: This diplomat has demonstrated a high level of capability in cooperation with foreign governments.
